---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "404 — Página no encontrada"
description: "Esta página no existe. O existió y ya no. O quizás nunca existió."
permalink: /404.html
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<div class="error-404 ancho">
  <div class="error-404__terminal">
    <div class="terminal__bar">
      <span class="terminal__dot terminal__dot--red"></span>
      <span class="terminal__dot terminal__dot--yellow"></span>
      <span class="terminal__dot terminal__dot--green"></span>
      <span class="terminal__title">paigar.es</span>
    </div>
    <div class="terminal__body">
      <p class="terminal__line"><span class="terminal__prompt">~</span> <span class="terminal__cmd">cat pagina.html</span></p>
      <p class="terminal__line"><span class="terminal__output terminal__output--error">Error: No such file or directory</span></p>
      <p class="terminal__line"><span class="terminal__prompt">~</span> <span class="terminal__cmd">echo $?</span></p>
      <p class="terminal__line"><span class="terminal__output">404</span></p>
      <p class="terminal__line"><span class="terminal__prompt">~</span><span class="terminal__cursor"></span></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="error-404__content">
    <h1 class="error-404__title">Página no encontrada</h1>
    <p class="error-404__text">La URL que buscas no existe. Puede que el enlace esté roto, que la página se haya movido, o que nunca haya existido.</p>
    <p class="error-404__text error-404__text--quote">Como diría Roy Batty: se perdió en el tiempo, como cookies en la red.</p>
    <div class="error-404__links">
      <a href="/" class="error-404__cta">Ir al inicio</a>
      <a href="/bitacora/" class="error-404__cta error-404__cta--ghost">Bitácora</a>
      <a href="/reflexiones/" class="error-404__cta error-404__cta--ghost">Reflexiones</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{%- css %}
.error-404 {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-2xl);
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  text-align: center;
}

/* ── Terminal (replica hero) ── */
.error-404__terminal {
  border-radius: var(--radius-l);
  overflow: hidden;
  background-color: var(--color-codigo-fondo);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-codigo-borde);
  box-shadow:
    0 4px 24px var(--color-sombra),
    0 0 60px var(--color-sombra-acento),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: var(--fs-1);
  line-height: 1.8;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 28rem;
  transition: box-shadow var(--transition-normal);
}

.error-404__terminal:hover {
  box-shadow:
    0 8px 40px var(--color-sombra),
    0 0 80px var(--color-sombra-acento),
    inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
}

.error-404 .terminal__bar {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  padding: 0.6rem 0.9rem;
  background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-codigo-borde);
}

.error-404 .terminal__dot {
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
  border-radius: 50%;
}
.error-404 .terminal__dot--red    { background: #ff5f57; }
.error-404 .terminal__dot--yellow { background: #febc2e; }
.error-404 .terminal__dot--green  { background: #28c840; }

.error-404 .terminal__title {
  margin-left: auto;
  font-size: var(--fs-2);
  color: var(--color-texto-alt);
  opacity: 0.5;
}

.error-404 .terminal__body {
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  text-align: left;
  background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(
    0deg,
    transparent,
    transparent 2px,
    rgba(0,0,0,0.08) 2px,
    rgba(0,0,0,0.08) 4px
  );
}

.error-404 .terminal__prompt {
  color: var(--color-acento);
  font-weight: 700;
}

.error-404 .terminal__cmd {
  color: #dcdcd4;
}

.error-404 .terminal__output {
  color: var(--color-codigo-texto);
}

.error-404 .terminal__output--error {
  color: #ff5f57;
}

.error-404 .terminal__cursor {
  display: inline-block;
  width: 0.55em;
  height: 1.1em;
  background-color: var(--color-acento);
  vertical-align: text-bottom;
  margin-left: 0.3em;
  animation: blink404 1s step-end infinite;
}

@keyframes blink404 {
  0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
  50%      { opacity: 0; }
}

/* ── Contenido ── */
.error-404__title {
  font-size: var(--fs5);
  font-weight: 800;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
}

.error-404__text {
  color: var(--color-texto-alt);
  max-width: 50ch;
  line-height: 1.6;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
}

.error-404__text--quote {
  font-style: italic;
  opacity: 0.8;
}

/* ── Botones ── */
.error-404__links {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-s);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  justify-content: center;
  margin-top: var(--space-l);
}

.error-404__cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5em;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: var(--fs-1);
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: 0.65em 1.3em;
  border-radius: var(--radius-m);
  background-color: var(--color-acento);
  color: #fff;
  transition: transform var(--transition-fast),
    box-shadow var(--transition-fast),
    background-color var(--transition-fast);
}

.error-404__cta:hover {
  background-color: var(--color-acento-hover);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 20px var(--color-sombra-acento);
}

.error-404__cta--ghost {
  background-color: transparent;
  color: var(--color-texto);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-borde);
}

.error-404__cta--ghost:hover {
  background-color: var(--color-fondo-alt);
  border-color: var(--color-acento);
  color: var(--color-acento);
  box-shadow: none;
}
{% endcss %}
